Title: A black hole hologram in de Sitter space
Authors: Ulf H. Danielsson
Comments: 13 pages. Final version accepted for publication in JHEP. Added
  references and improved presentation
Report-no: UUITP-06/01
Journal-ref: JHEP 0203 (2002) 020
\\
  In this paper we show that the entropy of de Sitter space with a black hole
in arbitrary dimension can be understood using a modified Cardy-Verlinde
entropy formula. We also comment on the observer dependence of the de Sitter
entropy.
